title: Piltover Icon
body: I remember clicking on the button that enables me to get it, but I never received the icon. Is there a reason for this?

replies.body: Players who were eligible for the Piltover icon have already received it.  Are you sure you were logged into the correct account at the time of redemption?  I don't really think we'd be able to assist at this point, but you can hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) just in case.  We'll look into your specific issue individually to see if we missed something.
Yes, probably the icons will be received after 2 feb
